== Rohingya ==
=== Noun ===
'''boda'''
#[[egg]]

=== Etymology ===
''Boda'' seems derived from Arabic word ''Béda''. <br>
''Andha'' is also another name for Egg in Rohingya Langauage. <br>
''Dimm'' is also another name for Egg but mostly used by Hindus migrated from India. <br>

